Task4-Given an array of integers and a positive ineteger K,write a program to find :The Kth smallest element

import java.util.Arrays;

class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] a = {7, 10, 4, 3, 20};
        int k = 3;

        Arrays.sort(a);

        System.out.println("Kth smallest element = " + a[k - 1]);
    }
}

Output:
Kth smallest element = 7
